{"word":"Nehemiah","slug":"nehemiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nehemiah</b> - \"The Patriotic Statesman\" Characteristics of<p/>Patriotism<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=1&verse=1'>Ne 1:1-4</a><p/>Prayerfulness<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=1&verse=5'>Neh 1:5-11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=4'>Neh 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=5'>Neh 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=9'>Neh 4:9</a><p/>Faith<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=20'>Neh 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=14'>Neh 4:14</a><p/>Courage<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=20'>Neh 4:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=10'>Neh 6:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=11'>Neh 6:11</a><p/>Diligence<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=21'>Neh 4:21-23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=3'>Neh 6:3</a><p/>Executive ability<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=13'>Ne 4:13-20</a><p/>Firmness in the right<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=11'>Neh 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=17'>Neh 13:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=25'>Neh 13:25</a><p/>Earnestness in reform<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=5&verse=1'>Neh 5:1-19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=15'>Neh 13:15-31</a>"}]}